<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>Document</title>
  <script src="https://kit.fontawesome.com/9bc9c7a1c8.js" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
</head>
<body>
<div class="container-fluid">
  <div class="container fill bg">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-md-8 offset-md-1">

        <p class="mt-4 note"> <%= UniversitiesProgram.count %> programs available</p>
        <h1 class="mt-0">Looking for your next studies?</h1>
        <p>Finding the right program for your studies requires special attention and takes an effort. <br>
        Use UNIFind to search for programs, track deadlines and organize your documents during the process.</p>




        <div class="my-container">
            <div class="box query-input">
              <%= form_tag universities_programs_path, method: :get do %>
              <div class="my-row">
                <div class="top-search d-flex justify-content-between align-self-stretch">
                  <%= text_field_tag :query,
                  params[:query], :class => "home-search-input w-100 mb-2", placeholder: "Program Name"%>
                  <%= submit_tag "Search", class: "btn btn-block primary-btn " %>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <% end %>
          </div>
          </div>
          <div id="hidden-search">
            <div class="results box">
              <div class="d-flex">
                <p class= 'search-header justify-content-start'>See all results</p>
                <i class="far fa-times-square" id="close"></i>
              </div>
              <div class="my-row">
                <div class="results d-flex justify-content-between">
                  <%= button_to 'All', universities_programs_path, method: :get, class: "secondary-btn" %>
                  <%#= link_to 'create goal', goals_path, method: :post %>

                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="cities box">
              <p class= 'search-header'>Most searched cities</p>
              <div class="my-row">
                <div class="cities small-btn d-flex justify-content-between">
                  <%= button_to 'Berlin', universities_programs_path, method: :get, params: {query: 'Berlin'}, class: "secondary-btn" %>
                  <%= button_to 'Cologne', universities_programs_path, method: :get, params: {query: 'Cologne'}, class: "secondary-btn" %>
                  <%= button_to 'Karlsruhe', universities_programs_path, method: :get, params: {query: 'Karlsruhe'}, class: "secondary-btn" %>
                  <%= button_to 'Munich', universities_programs_path, method: :get, params: {query: 'Munich'}, class: "secondary-btn" %>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="degrees box">
              <p class= 'search-header'>Select a degree</p>
              <div class="my-row">
                <div class="small-btn d-flex justify-content-between">
                  <%= button_to "Bachelor of Science", universities_programs_path, method: :get, params: {query: 'Bachelor of Science'}, class: "secondary-btn" %>
                  <%= button_to "Bachelor of Arts", universities_programs_path, method: :get, params: {query: 'Bachelor of Arts'}, class: "secondary-btn" %>
                  <%= button_to "Master's degree", universities_programs_path, method: :get, params: {query: 'Master'}, class: "secondary-btn" %>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

          </div>


        <div class="row mt-4 mb-4 transition1">
          <div class="col-md-8 mt-2">
            <h6>Most searched programs:</h6>
            <a href= "/universities_programs?query=medicine" class="tag-label">Medicine</a>
            <a href= "/universities_programs?query=engineering" class="tag-label">Engineering</a>
            <a href= "/universities_programs?query=archeology" class="tag-label">Archeology</a>
            <a href= "/universities_programs?query=product+design" class="tag-label">Product Design</a>
            <a href= "/universities_programs?query=literature" class="tag-label">Literature</a>
            <a href= "/universities_programs?query=preschool+teaching" class="tag-label">Preschool Teaching</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
<div class="container mt-5 transition2">
  <div class="row justify-content-md-center">
    <h3 class="col-md-auto">HOW TO GET STARTED</h3>
  </div>
  <div class="row justify-content-md-center">
    <h2 class="col-md-auto">Four simple steps to get going:</h2>
  </div>
  <div class="row justify-content-md-center">
    <p class="col-md-auto">Here we will write another value proposition.
    Also will be a general overview description of how the site is supposed to help people. (User Story)</p>
  </div>

  <div class="row justify-content-between">
    <div class="col-3">
      <div class="explore"></div>
      <h3 class="text-center">EXPLORE</h3>
      <p class="text-center">There are <%= UniversitiesProgram.count %> programs available in our system for the user waiting to be explored.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="col-3">
      <div class="learn"></div>
      <h3 class="text-center">LEARN</h3>
      <p class="text-center">Pretty much all the essential information will be found on the department page.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="col-3">
      <div class="follow"></div>
      <h3 class="text-center">FOLLOW</h3>
      <p class="text-center">We have to mention that we have created a handy dashboard for the user to list their desired programs.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="col-3">
      <div class="prepare"></div>
      <h3 class="text-center">PREPARE</h3>
      <p class="text-center">Make a collection of your preparation documents and track the progress  via a visualized tool.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="container mt-4">
    <div class="row justify-content-md-center">
      <h2 class="col-md-auto mt-4">List by discipline</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="row mt-2">
      <div class="col disc-icon"></div>
      <div class="col disc-icon"></div>
      <div class="col disc-icon"></div>
      <div class="col disc-icon"></div>
      <div class="col disc-icon"></div>
      <div class="col disc-icon"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="row mb-4">
      <div class="col disc-icon"></div>
      <div class="col disc-icon"></div>
      <div class="col disc-icon"></div>
      <div class="col disc-icon"></div>
      <div class="col disc-icon"></div>
      <div class="col disc-icon"></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
<body>
</html>
